总体上，约翰逊和利文斯通的施政内容无太大变化。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=373}}然而，他确实扭转了利文斯通政府实施的一系列措施，结束了该市与[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]的石油交易，关闭了公开发行的《{{le|伦敦人报|The Londoner}}》，并取消了黑色出租车的半年检，虽然后者在三年后又被恢复。{{sfnm|1a1=Edwards|1a2=Isaby|1y=2008|1p=211|2a1=Purnell|2y=2011|2p=373}}取消了伦敦西部收[[伦敦交通拥挤税|拥堵费]]的区域，{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=443}}还取消了对[[四轮驱动|四轮驱动]]的机动车增收拥堵费的计划。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=391}}他后来被指控没有出版关于大伦敦当局委托的空气污染的独立报告。这份报告后来于2013年发布，表明伦敦自2010年在433所小学所在的地区[[二氧化氮|二氧化氮]]的水平超标。贫困地区，如纽汉、哈克尼和哈姆莱茨大楼，平均比更富裕的地区污染严重，每年有6000名伦敦人死于高于欧盟标准的二氧化氮引起的并发症。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2015/jul/15/nearly-9500-people-die-each-year-in-london-because-of-air-pollution-study|title=Nearly 9,500 people die each year in London because of air pollution – study|work=The Guardian|date=2015-07-15|accessdate=2017-04-24|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206061903/https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2015/jul/15/nearly-9500-people-die-each-year-in-london-because-of-air-pollution-study|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2016/may/16/boris-johnson-accused-of-burying-study-linking-pollution-and-deprived-schools|title=Boris Johnson accused of burying study linking pollution and deprived schools|work=Guardian newspapers|author=Adam Vaughan|date=2016-05-16|accessdate=2016-08-22|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206061908/https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2016/may/16/boris-johnson-accused-of-burying-study-linking-pollution-and-deprived-schools|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=tele>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/05/17/boris-johndon-accused-of-hiding-study-linking-air-pollution-and/|title=Boris Johnson accused of hiding study linking air pollution and deprived schools|work=Daily Telegraph|date=2016-05-17|accessdate=2016-08-22|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206061922/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/05/17/boris-johndon-accused-of-hiding-study-linking-air-pollution-and/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/boris-johnson-accused-of-burying-report-on-the-number-of-deprived-schools-in-londons-most-polluted-a7033016.html|title=Boris Johnson accused of burying report on the number of schools in London's most polluted areas|work=The Independent|author=Caroline Mortimer|date=2016-05-16|accessdate=2017-04-24|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423070559/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/boris-johnson-accused-of-burying-report-on-the-number-of-deprived-schools-in-londons-most-polluted-a7033016.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他保留一些利文斯通的项目如[[橫貫鐵路|橫貫鐵路]]和[[2012年伦敦奥运会|2012年伦敦奥运会]]，但被指责试图将之归功于己。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=390}}他采用了利文斯顿政府所制定的公共自行车计划；通称为“[[桑坦德自行车|鲍里斯自行车]]”，部分通过私人融资系统融资1.4亿英镑资金造成了重大的经济损失，虽然它被证明很受欢迎。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mayorwatch.co.uk/exclusive-tfl-reveals-how-much-barclays-has-paid-for-cycle-hire-scheme/201223704/|title=Exclusive: TfL reveals how much Barclays has paid for Cycle Hire scheme|author=Martin Hoscik|work=MayorWatch|accessdate=2017-04-24|archive-date=2019-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720102134/https://www.mayorwatch.co.uk/exclusive-tfl-reveals-how-much-barclays-has-paid-for-cycle-hire-scheme/201223704/|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfnm|1a1=Purnell|1y=2011|1pp=414–416|2a1=Gimson|2y=2012|2p=307}}尽管约翰逊支持在伦敦骑自行车，他自己本身就是广为人知的自行车骑行者，他的政府被一些骑行者批评没有打造更安全的自行车骑行环境。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|pp=442–443}}根据其选举承诺，约翰逊委托开发在市中心运营的新伦敦巴士。{{sfnm|1a1=Purnell|1y=2011|1p=417|2a1=Gimson|2y=2012|2p=307}}他还命令建造连通[[格林威治半岛|格林威治半岛]]和皇家码头之间的[[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]缆车系统。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|pp=417–418}}在担任市长之初，约翰逊宣布计划将现付现收的[[蠔卡|蚝卡]]的适用范围扩展至伦敦的国家铁路服务，<ref name=es_oystersie>{{cite news |last=Waugh |first=Paul |title=Boris plans to 'Oysterise' overground rail services by next May |url=http://www.standard.co.uk/news/boris-plans-to-oysterise-overground-rail-services-by-next-may-6690497.html |accessdate=2013-11-21 |newspaper=London Evening Standard |date=2008-05-12 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129151729/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/boris-plans-to-oysterise-overground-rail-services-by-next-may-6690497.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>约翰逊选举宣言中的一个承诺是保留Tube售票处，反对利文斯通关闭多达40个伦敦地铁售票处的提议。<ref name=2008_transport_manifesto>{{cite news |last=Johnson |first=Boris |title=Saying No To Ticket Office Closures |url=http://image.guardian.co.uk/sys-files/Guardian/documents/2009/04/27/Transportmanifesto.pdf |work=Getting Londoners Moving (Transport Manifesto for the 2008 Mayoral election) |publisher=Back Boris campaign |accessdate=2013-11-21 |page=38 |archive-date=2010-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100423195938/http://image.guardian.co.uk/sys-files/Guardian/documents/2009/04/27/Transportmanifesto.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>2008年7月2日，市长办公室宣布关闭计划将被放弃，售票处将保持开放。<ref name=es_kenplan>{{cite news |last=Murray |first=Dick |title=Mayor scraps Ken plan to axe 40 Tube ticket offices |url=http://www.standard.co.uk/news/mayor-scraps-ken-plan-to-axe-40-tube-ticket-offices-6869816.html |accessdate=2013-11-21 |newspaper=London Evening Standard |date=2008-07-02 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903131630/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/mayor-scraps-ken-plan-to-axe-40-tube-ticket-offices-6869816.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年11月21日，[[伦敦交通局|伦敦交通局]]宣布所有伦敦地铁售票处将于2015年关闭。<ref name=bbc_borisplan>{{cite news |title=London Underground in 24-hour plans as ticket offices shut |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-25025888 |accessdate=2015-02-17 |date=2013-11-21 |publisher=BBC News |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206062019/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-25025888 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在资助这些项目时，约翰逊政府借贷了1亿英镑，{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=437}}而公共交通票价则增加了50％。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=416}}

5月4日约翰逊到任市长后，6日任命大伦敦议会保守党领袖{{le|理查德·巴恩斯|Richard Barnes (British politician)}}为{{le|副市长|Deputy Mayor of London}}，同时任命竞选团队主要成员、前伦敦治安负责人{{le|伊恩·克莱门特|Ian Clement}}为政府关系副市长，大伦敦议会议员[[基特·马特豪斯|基特·马特豪斯]]为治安副市长，青年工作者[[雷·刘易斯|雷·刘易斯]]为青年副市长，<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite press release |title=Boris Johnson announces further senior appointments to his administration |publisher=Greater London Authority |date=2008-05-06 |url=http://www.london.gov.uk/view_press_release.jsp?releaseid=16774 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080512115137/http://www.london.gov.uk/view_press_release.jsp?releaseid=16774 |archivedate=2008-05-12 |accessdate=2008-05-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{le|西蒙·弥尔顿|Simon Milton (politician)
}}爵士为政策和规划副市长兼市长幕僚长，<ref name="autogenerated1" />还任命{{le|马尼拉·米萨|Munira Mirza}}为市长文化顾问，“政策交流”智库创始人、牛津同学[[尼克·博尔斯|尼克·博尔斯]]担任市长幕僚长，<ref name="times20080511">{{cite news |title=Boris Tory HQ team puts reins on Boris Johnson |date=2008-05-11 |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/politics/article3908506.ece |accessdate=2008-05-11 |location=London |work=The Times |first1=Robert |last1=Watts |first2=Jonathan |last2=Oliver |archive-date=2011-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430100118/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/politics/article3908506.ece |dead-url=no }}{{subscription required}}</ref>反对者质疑约翰逊对到任两个月就因财务不当行为和虚假声明而辞职的副市长雷·刘易斯的判断。<ref name=lewis20080704>{{cite news |title=London mayor: Johnson forced to remove his deputy mayor after magistrate claim proves false |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2008-07-04 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2008/jul/05/boris.london |accessdate=2008-07-05 |first=Matthew |last=Taylor |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206062007/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2008/jul/05/boris.london |dead-url=no }}</ref>

