约翰逊的首个市长任期在某些问题上被认为偏左，例如通过支持伦敦[[维生工资|最低生活工资]]和大赦非法移民的想法。他试图通过伦敦的同性恋骄傲游行和赞美少数民族报纸来安抚批评家不要说他是怪胎。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|pp=374–375}}2012年他禁止基督教团体Core Issues Trust在公交车上刊登“同性恋是病”的广告。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/apr/12/anti-gay-adverts-boris-johnson |location=London |work=The Guardian |first1=Helene |last1=Mulholland |first2=Robert |last2=Booth |first3=Patrick |last3=Strudwick |title=Anti-gay adverts pulled from bus campaign by Boris Johnson |date=2012-04-12 |accessdate=2017-04-24 |archive-date=2020-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217103303/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/apr/12/anti-gay-adverts-boris-johnson |dead-url=no }}</ref>2008年8月，约翰逊打破官方不对外国选举表态的传统，公开认可[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]当选为[[美国总统|美国总统]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/global/2008/aug/01/boris.barackobama |title=Barack Obama gets backing from Boris Johnson |work=The Guardian |date=2008-08-01 |location=London |first=Hélène |last=Mulholland |accessdate=2010-04-01 |archive-date=2019-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720095111/https://www.theguardian.com/global/2008/aug/01/boris.barackobama |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/borisjohnson/2484162/Boris-Johnson-backs-Barack-Obama-as-US-President.html |title=Boris Johnson backs Barack Obama as US President |work=The Daily Telegraph |date=2008-08-01 |location=London |first=Rosa |last=Prince |accessdate=2010-04-01 |archive-date=2008-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080807023853/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/borisjohnson/2484162/Boris-Johnson-backs-Barack-Obama-as-US-President.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

约翰逊自领[[首都警察監管局|首都警察監管局]]主席，并于2008年10月成功地迫使[[大伦敦警察|大伦敦警察]]局长{{le|伊恩·布莱尔|Ian Blair}}辞职，后者因为据称将合同交给朋友和处理巴西公民[[琼·查尔斯·德梅内塞斯|琼·查尔斯·德梅内塞斯]]的死亡案而受到批评。{{sfnm|1a1=Purnell|1y=2011|1pp=377–278|2a1=Gimson|2y=2012|2p=304}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/7648664.stm |publisher=BBC News |title=Britain's top policeman resigns |date=2008-10-02 |accessdate=2010-04-01 |archive-date=2020-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423070657/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/7648664.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/uk/crime/article4868974.ece |work=The Times |location=London |title=Boris Johnson forces Sir Ian Blair to quit as police chief |first1=Sean |last1=O'Neill |first2=Adam |last2=Fresco |first3=Sam |last3=Coates |date=2008-10-03 |accessdate=2010-04-01}} {{subscription required}}</ref>这使约翰逊赢得了保守党的尊重，他们把此事解释为约翰逊的第一个充满力量和自信的处置。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=379}}虽然2010年1月他辞去首都警察監管局主席职务，{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=388}}在其市长任内，约翰逊高度支持大伦敦警察，特别是在围绕{{le|伊恩·汤姆林森死亡|Death of Ian Tomlinson}}的争论中。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|pp=387–388}}伦敦的整体犯罪率下降，尽管约翰逊认为严重的青少年犯罪减少，但这种说法被证明是错的，因为它增加了。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=436}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-15765557 |title=London mayor admits 'caveats' in youth crime statistics |authorlink=Tim Donovan |author=Donovan, Tim |publisher=BBC News |date=2011-11-16 |accessdate=2017-04-24 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206062050/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-15765557 |dead-url=no }}</ref>同样，他声称大伦敦警察队伍扩大的说法也不正确，因为该市的警察规模在其管理下减少，与英国其他地方一致。{{sfn|Purnell|2011|p=436}}[[2011年英国骚乱|2011年英国骚乱]]发生时，约翰逊和家人正在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[不列颠哥伦比亚省|不列颠哥伦比亚省]]度假，他没有立刻回伦敦，而是骚乱发生两天后才启程回国，他因此受到批评。在访问[[克拉珀姆|克拉珀姆]]的受害地时，他被围观的人讥讽嘲笑。{{sfnm|1a1=Purnell|1y=2011|1pp=429–432|2a1=Gimson|2y=2012|2pp=333–335}}

