2013年2月，在2014年伦敦预算公布后的一次伦敦议会上，约翰逊表决后被迫退出会议，理由是他的副市长{{le|维多利亚·波雷克|Victoria Borwick}}离开了议事厅。当得知投票结果意味着他不用就预算回答议员的问题后，他说自己的反对者：“非常懒的无脊椎果冻”。<ref>{{cite news |last=Williams |first=Rob |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/video-great-supine-protoplasmic-invertebrate-jellies--boris-johnsons-parting-shot-at-london-assembly-members-after-they-vote-not-to-grill-him-over-16bn-budget-cut-8510244.html |title=Video: 'Great supine protoplasmic invertebrate jellies!' – Boris Johnson's parting shot at London Assembly members after they vote NOT to grill him over budget cuts |work=The Independent |location=London |date=2013-02-25 |accessdate=2013-05-21 |archive-date=2013-04-20 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130420130917/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/video-great-supine-protoplasmic-invertebrate-jellies--boris-johnsons-parting-shot-at-london-assembly-members-after-they-vote-not-to-grill-him-over-16bn-budget-cut-8510244.html }}</ref>

