g/web/20210206063234/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/boris-johnson-comments-burka-niqab-theresa-may-muslim-women-islam-latest-a8481666.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 一些保守党议员如[[娜汀·多里斯|娜汀·多里斯]]认为约翰逊的批评还不到位，他们认为罩袍应被禁止。<ref>{{cite news |title=Conservative chairman calls for apology from Boris Johnson over burka remarks |url=http://home.bt.com/news/uk-news/conservative-chairman-calls-for-apology-from-boris-johnson-over-burka-remarks-11364287913473 |work=BT News |date=2018-08-07 |accessdate=2019-05-25 |archive-date=2020-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605161822/http://home.bt.com/news/uk-news/conservative-chairman-calls-for-apology-from-boris-johnson-over-burka-remarks-11364287913473 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 一项[[天空新闻|天空新闻]]民意调查发现，60％的人认为约翰逊的言论并非种族主义，而33％的人认为是；48%的受访者认为约翰逊应该道歉，43%认为不必。<ref>{{cite news|title=Sky Data poll: Comparing women who wear burkas to bank robbers 'not racist'|url=https://news.sky.com/story/sky-data-poll-comparing-women-who-wear-burkas-to-bank-robbers-not-racist-11465688|publisher=Sky News|date=2018-08-08|accessdate=2018-08-09|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206063236/https://news.sky.com/story/sky-data-poll-comparing-women-who-wear-burkas-to-bank-robbers-not-racist-11465688|dead-url=no}}</ref> 一个独立小组被组建起来以审查约翰逊的言论。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-45130532|title=Johnson to be investigated over burka row|date=2018-08-09|work=BBC News|access-date=2018-08-09|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206063241/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-45130532|dead-url=no}}</ref> 12月，小组认为约翰逊并无不法行为，虽然他的语言可以被认为是“挑衅”，但基于“尊重和宽容”，他完全有权使用“讽刺”来表达自己的观点。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.sky.com/story/boris-johnson-cleared-by-investigation-into-burka-comments-11587680|title=Boris Johnson cleared by investigation into burka comments|publisher=Sky News|access-date=2018-12-21|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206063316/https: