l=http://ria.ru/world/20150215/1047774674.html |title=Мэр Лондона намерен отказаться от гражданства США |trans-title=The Mayor of London is going to give up his US citizenship |date=2015-02-15 |agency=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]] |accessdate=2015-02-15 |language=ru |archive-date=2018-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709215701/https://ria.ru/world/20150215/1047774674.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年2月，据报道他在2016年正式放弃了美国国籍。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/feb/08/boris-johnson-renounces-us-citizenship-record-2016-uk-foreign-secretary|title=Boris Johnson among record number to renounce US citizenship in 2016|date=2017-02-08|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2017-02-09|archive-date=2019-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190722082219/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/feb/08/boris-johnson-renounces-us-citizenship-record-2016-uk-foreign-secretary|dead-url=no}}</ref>

